 本帖最后由 暗夜之猫 于 2014-5-23 19:07 编辑 

增加权限要用到Groupmanager，必须在库中添加Groupmanager.jar
定义class变量:
User user;
OverloadedWorldHolder dataHolder = null;

在onCommand函数中:

Player player = (Player)sender;
this.dataHolder = this.worldsHolder.getWorldData(player);

user = this.dataHolder.getUser(用户名);
user.addPermission(权限名称);
